## Note on Individual Skill Licenses

The SKILL.md files in this repository originate from 56 different GitHub
repositories, each with its own license. The MIT license above applies to the
scripts, catalog data, audit reports, and documentation created by this project.

Individual SKILL.md files retain the license specified in their YAML frontmatter
`license` field. If no license field is present, the original repository's
license applies. Please check the `license` and `metadata.source_repo` fields
in each SKILL.md before redistribution.
